data.name: lblWelcomeImport.Text
data.value:
It's very similar to creating a trigger. After this screen, you can select the folder where you want to import all the triggers to (or Root), and then hit the Import button on the top bar.
This is the button you should be looking out for:

data.name: lblWelcomeStart.Text
data.value:
When you start Triggernometry for the first time, you will generally see an empty view with "Local Triggers" and "Remote Triggers".
To access a lot of premade triggers for Triggernometry, you can right-click on "Remote Triggers", and choose to add a repository from list:
